# Agent Workflow

Pause and ask for user confirmation before:

- Adding new pages or major features
- Refactoring shared components (`DataTable`, `PageShell`, `FormSheet`, etc.)
- Deviating from established UI patterns in `.cursor/rules/ui-patterns.mdc`
- Broad architectural changes

Routine bug fixes and small edits within an established pattern do not require confirmation.
